headline.print_headline: Monique Lhuillier Shows Delicate Beading, Pastels
headline.main: Monique Lhuillier Shows Delicate Beading, Pastels

lead_paragraph: Delicate beading on evening dresses in muted pastels were juxtaposed with a lot of shimmer and full puffy quilted skirting Friday on the Mercedes-Benz Fashion Week runway of Monique Lhuillier.
